skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Get weekly travel tips and inspirations that will get you physically, mentally, and emotionally ready to take your next trip! Even without a trip in the near future, this skill will keep you in the mindset of a traveler. Be free, curious, and adventurous! Enjoy the journey.

Listen to weekly travel tips and inspirations from your favorite travel lover and expert at Kaleidoscope Travel. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.

This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
